OL,3,CHosepipe ban comes into force as third
OL,4,Cheatwave hits
OL,6,FAround a million Southern Water
OL,7,Fcustomers are now banned from using
OL,8,Fhosepipes across Hampshire and the
OL,9,FIsle of Wight.
OL,11,FOfficials warn that drought conditions
OL,12,Fare increasingly likely while the
OL,13,Fnation swelters in another lengthy
OL,14,Fheatwave.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
