OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783786689
OL,3,CHosepipe ban comes into force as third
OL,4,Cheatwave hits
OL,6,FAnother record tumbled on Thursday, 9
OL,7,FJuly, when the UK recorded its eighth
OL,8,Fday at or above 34C in a calendar
OL,9,Fyear, reaching 34.4C at Wisley in
OL,10,FSurrey, breaking the previous high of
OL,11,Fseven days set in the summer of 1976
OL,12,Fand in 2020.
OL,14,FFrom today, Friday 10 July, people
OL,15,Facross Hampshire and the Isle of Wight
OL,16,Fwill not be allowed to use hosepipes
OL,17,Ffor watering gardens, washing cars or
OL,18,Ffilling swimming and paddling pools.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
