OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783786689
OL,3,CHosepipe ban comes into force as third
OL,4,Cheatwave hits
OL,6,FThe River Test is one of the world's
OL,7,Frarest chalk streams and supplies most
OL,8,Fof the water to homes and businesses
OL,9,Fin Hampshire and the Isle of Wight.
OL,11,FFollowing the warmest spring on record
OL,12,Fand record-breaking heatwaves, river
OL,13,Flevels are now critically low, down 25
OL,14,Fper cent on what is normal for this
OL,15,Ftime of year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
