OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783786689
OL,3,CHosepipe ban comes into force as third
OL,4,Cheatwave hits
OL,6,FTania Flasck, Director of Water
OL,7,FOperations at Southern Water, said:
OL,8,F"We're working round the clock to keep
OL,9,Ftaps flowing and protect the River
OL,10,FTest, which is at a critically low
OL,11,Flevel following recent hot weather.
OL,13,F"We'll continue to do everything we
OL,14,Fcan to ensure our pipes, reservoirs
OL,15,Fand water supply works are working as
OL,16,Fefficiently as possible - but that
OL,17,Fwon't be enough.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783786689
OL,3,CHosepipe ban comes into force as third
OL,4,Cheatwave hits
OL,6,F"I want to thank people for the
OL,7,Fincredible efforts they made last year
OL,8,Fto save water during the hosepipe ban.
OL,9,FTheir actions really made a difference.
OL,11,F"By working together, we can ensure we
OL,12,Fkeep the taps flowing, protect the
OL,13,Fenvironment and reduce pressure on the
OL,14,FRiver Test."
OL,16,FA hosepipe uses 1,000 litres of water
OL,17,Fan hour ` that's one person's weekly
OL,18,Fwater use in just 60 minutes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
