OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783786689
OL,3,CHosepipe ban comes into force as third
OL,4,Cheatwave hits
OL,6,FSouthern Water says simple swaps like
OL,7,Fusing a watering can or bucket instead
OL,8,Fwill bring usage down quickly.
OL,10,FThere are exemptions to the ban,
OL,11,Fincluding for Priority Services
OL,12,FRegister and WaterSure customers with
OL,13,Fmobility or health needs, such as Blue
OL,14,FBadge holders.
OL,16,FThe Environment Agency is moving parts
OL,17,Fof Hampshire and the Isle of Wight
OL,18,Finto a state of prolonged dry weather
OL,19,Fafter England's warmest spring on
OL,20,Frecord.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
