OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783786689
OL,3,CHosepipe ban comes into force as third
OL,4,Cheatwave hits
OL,6,FRichard O'Callaghan, Environment
OL,7,FPlanning & Engagement manager at the
OL,8,FEnvironment Agency said:
OL,10,F"The changing climate has seen a
OL,11,Fwhiplash from an exceptionally wet
OL,12,Fstart of the year to prolonged dry
OL,13,Fweather.
OL,15,F"The pressures on the environment will
OL,16,Fbecome heavier. The Environment Agency
OL,17,Fis positioning itself to get ahead of
OL,18,Fthat.
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783786689
OL,3,CHosepipe ban comes into force as third
OL,4,Cheatwave hits
OL,6,F"We are ready to tackle any incidents
OL,7,Fduring this time and make sure that
OL,8,Fthe needs of the environment are
OL,9,Fbalanced against demands for more
OL,10,Fwater from our most sensitive
OL,11,Fwaterways."
OL,13,FIn 2025, the dry spring, early summer
OL,14,Fand high temperatures affected water
OL,15,Fresources and the environment in
OL,16,FHampshire, Isle of Wight and Sussex,
OL,17,Fleading to the Environment Agency
OL,18,Fdeclaring a situation of prolonged dry
OL,19,Fweather lasting six months.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
