OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783786689
OL,3,CHosepipe ban comes into force as third
OL,4,Cheatwave hits
OL,6,FThe National Drought Group - which
OL,7,Fincludes the Met Office, government,
OL,8,Fregulators, water companies, the
OL,9,FNational Farmers' Union, Canal & River
OL,10,FTrust, anglers, and conservation
OL,11,Fexperts ` is monitoring the situation
OL,12,Fand will next meet on 20 July.
OL,14,FThere are simple ways people can help
OL,15,Fsave water, including low-flow
OL,16,Fshowerheads, running washing machines
OL,17,Fwith the recommended load and not pre-
OL,18,Frinsing dishes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
