OL,3,CHosepipe ban comes into force as third
OL,4,Cheatwave hits
OL,6,FFor the Environment Agency's Solent
OL,7,Fand South Downs operational area, the
OL,8,Fmonthly rainfall figures and their
OL,9,Flong-term average for 2026 were:
OL,11,FSouth East Water introduced a ban on
OL,12,FJuly 3 for areas of Kent, including
OL,13,Fthose in Ashford, Canterbury,
OL,14,FFaversham, Maidstone, Sevenoaks,
OL,15,FSnodland, Tenterden and Tunbridge
OL,16,FWells.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
