OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783786689
OL,3,CHosepipe ban comes into force as third
OL,4,Cheatwave hits
OL,6,FAffinity Water has announced that it
OL,7,Fwill introduce a hosepipe ban on July
OL,8,F17, affecting more than three million
OL,9,Fcustomers including those in
OL,10,FBerkshire, Buckinghamshire, Essex and
OL,11,FSurrey.
OL,13,FWessex Water and Portsmouth Water are
OL,14,Falso urging customers to use water
OL,15,Fwisely amid the heatwave.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/11
